<p>Start with review requests. Online reviews are the highest-ROI marketing asset for local businesses. 98% of consumers read them before making a decision. A simple automated SMS after each service, with a direct Google review link, generates consistent reviews with zero ongoing effort. Add appointment reminders as your second automation.</p>
